Ethe%20PGA%20Tour%20and%20the%20Saudi-backed%20LIV%20Golf%20league%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20negotiation%20points%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpga-tour-merger-liv-golf-congress-hearing-saudi-arabia-2023-7%5C%22%3EPGA%20Tour%20officials%20were%20hauled%20in%20front%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20US%20Senate%20Permanent%20Subcommittee%20on%20Investigations%20for%20a%20three-hour%20hearing%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-pga-tour-merged-liv-golf-commissioner-jay-monahan-report-2023-6%5C%22%3Eannounced%20merger%20with%20LIV%20Golf%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20the%20role%20the%20Saudi%20Arabian%20Public%20Investment%20Fund%20(PIF)%20would%20have%20in%20the%20combined%20league.%20The%20PGA%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20despite%20the%20fanfare%2C%20the%20initial%20announcement%20of%20a%20deal%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20was%20premature%20and%20negotiations%20are%20still%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20PGA%20Tour%20board%20member%20Jimmy%20Dunne%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20simply%20an%20agreement%20to%20try%20to%20get%20to%20an%20agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20billions%20of%20dollars%20on%20the%20line%2C%20the%20deal%20doesn't%20sound%20like%20a%20sure%20thing%20at%20all%2C%20but%20the%20hearing%20did%20offer%20some%20interesting%20tidbits%20about%20what%20the%20combined%20tour%20would%20look%20like%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiger%20Woods%20and%20Rory%20McIlroy%20would%20be%20given%20ownership%20of%20two%20teams%20in%20LIV%20Golf%20and%20they%20would%20commit%20to%20playing%20in%2010%20LIV%20events.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20%26quot%3BWorld%20Golf%20Series%26quot%3B%20team%20event%20would%20be%20held%20every%20year%C2%A0with%20the%20championship%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20PGA%20Tour%20events%20would%20be%20sponsored%20by%20either%20Aramco%2C%20the%20Saudi%20oil%20giant%2C%20or%20the%20PIF.%20One%20of%20those%20would%20be%20played%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELIV%20Golf%20players%20would%20be%20given%20points%20in%20the%20Official%20World%20Golf%20Rankings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELIV%20Golf%20would%20only%20play%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20not%20overlap%20with%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20PGA%20Tour%20season.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%20the%20most%20bizarre%20ask%20from%20the%20PIF%20that%20was%20revealed%20during%20the%20hearing%20has%20to%20do%20with%20PIF%20governor%20Yasir%20Al-Rumayyan%2C%20the%20LIV%20Golf%20chairman.%20According%20to%20the%20documents%20obtained%20by%20Congress%2C%20the%20head%20of%20PIF%20wants%20a%20green%20jacket%2C%20which%20is%20given%20to%20members%20of%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Club.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%2C%20Yasir%20Al-Rumayyan%2C%20and%20Greg%20Norman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64aea1918ed31300199e9630%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYasir%20Al-Rumayyan%20(center)%2C%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20(left)%20and%20Greg%20Norman%2C%20will%20never%20win%20a%20green%20jacket%2C%20but%20he%20wants%20one.%3Cp%3EChris%20Trotman%2FLIV%20Golf%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20documents%20sent%20to%20Congress%2C%20one%20of%20the%20requests%20from%20the%20PIF%20was%20for%20the%20PGA%20to%20try%20and%20get%20Al-Rumayyan%20membership%20at%20the%20legendary%20Augusta%20National%20Golf%20Cub%20and%20The%20Royal%20and%20Ancient%20Golf%20Club%20of%20St%20Andrews.%20What%20makes%20the%20demand%20even%20stranger%20is%20that%20the%20PGA%20Tour%20almost%20certainly%20does%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20grant%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PGA%20has%20close%20ties%20to%20both%20venues%20%E2%80%94%20Augusta%20National%20famously%20hosts%20the%20Masters%20every%20year%2C%20and%20St.%20Andrews%20is%20part%20of%20the%20rotation%20for%20hosting%20The%20Open%20Championship%20in%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20private%20golf%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-augusta-national-golf-club-the-masters-tournament-2018-3%5C%22%3EAs%20Business%20Insider's%20Stephanie%20Asymkos%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Augusta%20National%20is%20likely%20the%20most%20exclusive%20golf%20club%20in%20the%20US%20and%20its%20membership%20is%20shrouded%20in%20mystery.%20It%20is%20believed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmasters-tickets-lottery%5C%22%3Ethere%20are%20only%20about%20300%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20new%20memberships%20are%20typically%20reserved%20for%20when%20somebody%20leaves%20or%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20seek%20membership%20at%20Augusta%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Augusta%20wants%20you%2C%20it%20will%20find%20you.%20There's%20no%20waitlist.%20It's%20well-known%20among%20the%20golf%20community%20that%20if%20the%20Augusta%20powers%20that%20be%20so%20much%20as%20hear%20an%20expression%20of%20membership%20interest%2C%20that's%20enough%20to%20get%20your%20name%20permanently%20crossed%20off%20of%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPIF%20already%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.golfmonthly.com%2Fnews%2Fwho-is-yasir-al-rumayyan-liv-golf-chairman-and-public-investment-fund-governor%5C%22%3Einvestments%20in%20Uber%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Boeing%2C%20Disney%2C%20and%20the%20English%20Premier%20League%20soccer%20club%20Newcastle%20United%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Al-Rumayyan%20is%20the%20chairman.%20Gaining%20membership%20to%20Augusta%20National%20not%20only%20grants%20him%20entry%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20exclusive%20sports%20groups%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20also%20another%20way%20to%20access%20the%20other%20members%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamous-wall-street-augusta-national-members-2011-4%5C%22%3Ewhich%20include%20many%20business%20leaders%20and%