.%20It%20marks%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20SpiceJet%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20sustained%20growth%20and%20long-term%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JOY%20SENGUPTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fspicejet-promoter-ajay-singh-to-infuse-rs-500cr-into-spicejet%2Farticleshow%2F101702522.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Mishra%2C%20The%20Man%20Who%20Investigated%20Many%20VIPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20declared%20as%20illegal%20the%20third%20extension%20given%20to%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20chief%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20which%20was%20widely%20challenged%2C%20and%20said%20he%20cannot%20continue%20beyond%20July%2031.%20The%20move%20has%20brought%20into%20focus%20the%20life%20and%20work%20of%20an%20officer%20who%20became%20central%20to%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20called%20its%20crackdown%20on%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%201984-batch%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20officer%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20SK%20Mishra%2C%2063%2C%20was%20first%20appointed%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20for%20a%20stipulated%20period%20of%20two%20years%20in%202018%2C%20but%20he%20was%20given%20three%20extensions%20by%20the%20government.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20government%20last%20year%20brought%20an%20ordinance%20that%20said%20the%20term%20of%20directors%20of%20probe%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20CBI%20could%20be%20extended%20by%20up%20to%20three%20years%20after%20the%20mandated%20term%20of%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%2C%20during%20his%20tenure%20of%20five%20years%20till%20now%2C%20tightened%20scrutiny%20on%20many%20former%20ministers%20and%20powerful%20leaders%2C%20with%20the%20probe%20agency%20registering%204%2C000%20cases%2C%20and%20conducting%203%2C000%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20under%20Mr%20Mishra%20as%20chief%20that%20the%20ED%20investigated%20politicians%20like%20former%20finance%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20Karnataka%20Congress%20chief%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20NCP%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Deshmukh%2C%20another%20minister%20Nawab%20Malik%2C%20National%20Conference%20leaders%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20powerful%20minister%20Senthil%20Balaji%2C%20and%20former%20Trinamool%20Congress%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ED's%20actions%20met%20strong%20resistance%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20termed%20it%20harassment%20and%20misuse%20of%20power%2C%20the%20courts%20did%20not%20strike%20down%20the%20action%20taken%20under%20Mr%20Mishra%20or%20find%20fault%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency's%20actions%20implicitly%20boosted%20support%20for%20the%20government%20and%20made%20good%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20promise%20of%20%26quot%3BNa%20Khaoonga%2C%20na%20khane%20doonga%26quot%3B%20(I%20won't%20allow%20corruption).%20But%20the%20organisation%20also%20became%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20opposition's%20charge%20of%20the%20Centre%20misusing%20its%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Mishra's%20watch%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20roped%20in%20experts%2C%20trained%20professionals%20and%20even%20handled%20a%20multitude%20of%20high-profile%20cases%20-%20something%20only%20the%20CBI%20was%20known%20to%20do%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20have%20worked%20with%20him%20describe%20Mr%20Mishra%20as%20someone%20forgets%20nothing%20about%20any%20case%20he%20is%20handling%2C%20focuses%20on%20the%20smallest%20of%20details%2C%20and%20expects%20his%20team%20to%20always%20be%20on%20its%20toes.%20He%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20man%20with%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20understanding%20the%20nexus%20of%20politics%20and%20business%2C%20and%20someone%20who%20understands%20taxation%2C%20matters%20related%20to%20economics%20and%20foreign%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20goes%20after%20the%20corrupt%20with%20a%20thoroughly%20professional%20approach%2C%20addressing%20all%20loopholes%20in%20procedures%2C%20as%20any%20seasoned%20bureaucrat%20should.%20He%20doesn't%20'network'%20with%20politicians%20or%20leave%20any%20scope%20of%20an%20'understanding'%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20has%20been%20here%20all%20these%20years.%20He%20has%20a%20strong%20memory%2C%20so%20it%20helps%20to%20get%20things%20moving%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20belongs%20to%20a%20middle-class%20family%20based%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20He%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20science%20research%20and%20has%20a%20degree%20in%20biochemistry%20from%20the%20Lucknow%20University.%20As%20the%20Chief%20Commissioner%20of%20Income%20Tax%2C%20he%20investigated%20several%20high-level%20cases%20in%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20before%20he%20became%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20His%20investigation%20into%20Young%20India%2C%20a%20Gandhi%20family-run%20organisation%20that%20owns%20the%20National%20Herald%20newspaper%2C%20brought%20him%20into%20the%20spotlight%2C%20after%20which%20he%20took%20over%20as%20ED%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20under%20Mr.%20Mishra's%20tenure%20that%20the%20ED%20launched%20a%20probe%20against%20Congress%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20husband%20Robert%20Vadra.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20spent%20close%20to%2042%20hours%20over%20five%20days%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%2013%20hours%20over%20three%20days%2C%20at%20the%20ED%20office%2C%20answering%20questions%20in%20the%20National%20Herald%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra's%20tenure%20also%20saw%20the%20strict%20implementation%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20the%20Fugitive%20Economic%20Offenders%20Act%20brought%20by%20the%20Modi%20Government%20in%202018%2C%20and%20the%20civil%20sections%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20many%20petitions%20filed%20by%20political%20leaders%20challenging%20the%20extension%20given%20to%20Mr%20Mishra%2C%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20new%20person%20might%20take%20time%20to%20acclimatise%20to%20the%20working%20of%20the%20new%20organisation.%20The%20government%20defended%20its%20move%20to%20award%20multiple%20extensions%20to%20Mr%20Mishra%20saying%20it%20was%20done%20in%20public%20interest%20as%20various%20cases%20were%20at%20a%20crucial%20juncture%20and%20for%20their%20proper%20and%20expeditious%20disposal%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20ensure%20the%20continuity%20of%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mr%20Mishra's%20tenure%2C%20the%20agency%20also%20deported%20the%20VVIP%20choppers%20case%20accused%20and%20the%20alleged%20middlemen%20Christian%20Michel%20and%20Rajiv%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689167760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F5hai3dco_sk-mishra-_625x300_17_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-sanjay-kumar-mishra-the-man-who-investigated-many-vips-4201105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20declared%20as%20illegal%20the%20third%20extension%20given%20to%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20chief%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20which%20was%20widely%20challenged%2C%20and%20said%20he%20cannot%20continue%20beyond%20July%2031.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fenforcement-directorate-chief-sanjay-kumar-mishra-the-man-who-investigated-many-vips-4201105%22%2C%22cdnA