very%20issue%20did%20not%20go%20well%20with%20a%20section%20of%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20TMC%2C%20the%20result%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-birbhum-tmc-left-anubrata-mondal%5C%22%3EBirbhum%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20vindication%20of%20its%20organisational%20strength.%20The%20district%20head%20of%20the%20party%2C%20Anubrata%20Mondal%2C%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20on%20corruption%20charges.%20Sukdev%20Konda%2C%20a%20farmer%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20won%20in%20our%20area%20last%20time.%20But%20they%20claimed%20that%20they%20could%20not%20do%20development%20work%20as%20the%20state%20government%20did%20not%20cooperate.%20Work%20was%20stalled%20in%20our%20area.%20So%20we%20voted%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20get%20the%20work%20done.%20If%20they%20control%20the%20panchayat%2C%20we%20will%20receive%20cash%20transfers%20from%20various%20schemes%20along%20with%20Lakshmi%20Bhandar%20%5Bscheme%2C%20which%20gives%20financial%20support%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20families%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20panchayat%20performance%20will%20put%20a%20question%20on%20the%20mission%20to%20win%2035%20of%20the%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20election.%20The%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20main%20opposition%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20and%20campaigned%20extensively%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20in%20the%20strongholds%20of%20several%20top%20leaders%2C%20the%20party%20performed%20poorly.%20Dakshin%20Dinajpur%2C%20the%20home%20district%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20BJP%20state%20president%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%2C%20the%20TMC%20won%2054%20out%20of%2064%20gram%20panchayats.%20The%20former%20state%20chief%20and%20MP%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20hails%20from%20the%20rural%20Khara