aming%20the%20Congress-Left%20alliance%20for%20splitting%20opposition%20votes%20but%20they%20also%20admit%20the%20need%20for%20introspection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20were%20hoping%20for%20a%20resurgence%20after%20the%20humiliation%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections.%20While%20their%20vote%20share%20and%20number%20of%20winning%20seats%20have%20increased%20marginally%2C%20they%20were%20still%20far%20behind%20the%20BJP.%20The%20silver%20lining%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20its%20performance%20in%20Malda%20and%20Murshidabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Ramchandra%20Dome%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20CPI(M)%20politburo%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20only%207%25%20votes%20in%20the%20last%20two%20elections.%20Our%20vote%20share%20has%20significantly%20increased.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20for%20our%20ally%20Congress.%20With%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20dipping%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20a%20section%20of%20people%20who%20thought%20the%20BJP%20was%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20TMC%20have%20now%20returned%20to%20us.%20However%2C%20the%20polarisation%20among%20a%20section%20of%20tribals%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%20is%20clearly%20visible%2C%20which%20is%20dangerous.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%20performs%20well%20in%20North%20Bengal%20and%20Jungle%20Mahal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20TMC%20was%20able%20to%20do%20well%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20of%20North%20Bengal%20and%20Jungle%20Mahal.%20Despite%20vote%20boycotts%20and%20protests%2C%20a%20section%20of%20Kurmi%20votes%20in%20Jungle%20Mahal%20went%20to%20the%20TMC.%20In%20Dooars%2C%20the%20reopening%20of%20closed%20tea%20gardens%20and%20the%20Cha%20Sundari%20housing%20project%20clearly%20influenced%20the%20tea%20workers%2C%20which%20explained%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20Alipurduar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajbanshi-dominated%20area%20of%20North%20Bengal%2C%20Kamtapuri%20leader%20Banshivadan%20Barman%E2%80%99s%20direct%20support%20to%20the%20TMC%20caused%20the%20BJP%20major%20damage.%20Even%20after%20announcing%20the%20nomination%20for%20another%20Rajbanshi%20leader%2C%20Anant%20Maharaj%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20retain%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20North%20Bengal%20development%20minister%20Udayan%20Guha%2C%20a%20key%20architect%20of%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20challenge%20was%20to%20check%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise.%20He%20claimed%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20entered%20strong%20rooms%20at%20midnight%20and%20brought%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20mercenaries%20from%20Assam%E2%80%9D%20to%20attack%20people.%20Such%20tactics%2C%20he%20said%2C%20saw%20the%20people%20reject%20the%20saffron%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20claimed%20that%20the%20minority%20vote%20is%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20TMC.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20minority%20vote%20bank%20of%20Trinamool%20has%20broken!%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20bloodiest%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20panchayat%20poll%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20bloodiest%20ones%2C%20with%20clashes%20between%20the%20political%20parties%20causing%20the%20loss%20of%20at%20least%2040%20lives.%20The%20state%20election%20commission%20and%20the%20administration%20came%20under%20criticism%20for%20failing%20to%20stop%20malpractices.%20In%20Bali%2C%20Howrah%2C%20many%20ballots%20with%20the%20CPI(M)%20stamp%20were%20seen%20floating%20in%20sewage%20lines.%20Opposition%20agents%20were%20allegedly%20beaten%20and%20threatened%20by%20the%20TMC%20workers%20with%20the%20help%20of%20police%20at%20counting%20centres.%20A%20candidate%20named%20Habib%20Ali%20was%20beaten%20unconscious%20inside%20t