dnesday%20said%20that%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20the%20declaration%20of%20results%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20its%20final%20orders%20in%20connection%20with%20matters%20which%20it%20is%20hearing%20over%20allegations%20of%20electoral%20malpractices%20on%20the%20day%20of%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20central%20government%20to%20file%20affidavits%20dealing%20with%20all%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20three%20petitions%20alleging%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20court%20is%20seized%20of%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20whatever%20has%20been%20done%20thus%20far%2C%20i.e%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20elections%20and%20the%20declaration%20of%20results%2C%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20ultimate%20orders%20that%20may%20be%20passed%20in%20this%20writ%20petition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20that%20the%20SEC%20should%20inform%20this%20aspect%20to%20all%20the%20candidates%20who%20have%20been%20declared%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20large-scale%20violence%20and%20electoral%20malpractice%20during%20the%20panchayat%20election%20on%20July%208%2C%20the%20petitioners%20prayed%20for%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20SEC%20to%20conduct%20repolling%20in%20around%2050%2C000%20booths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepolling%20was%20done%20in%20696%20booths%20and%20counting%20of%20ballots%20began%20on%20July%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20petitioner%20who%20displayed%20videos%20showing%20alleged%20rampant%20malpractices%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20election%20was%20directed%20to%20furnish%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20videos%20to%20the%20lawyers%20of%20the%20SEC%2C%20the%20state%20and%20the%20central%20governments%20by%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20that%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20hearing%20on%20July%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20SEC%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20it%20is%20of%20prima%20facie%20view%20that%20the%20response%20from%20the%20Commission%20is%20not%20adequate%20and%20that%20even%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20none%20of%20its%20officers%20was%20present%20in%20the%20court%20to%20give%20necessary%20instructions%20to%20its%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20commission%20is%20not%20proactive%20especially%20when%20the%20court%20had%20been%20monitoring%20the%20entire%20process%20and%20the%20first%20judgement%20was%20delivered%20on%20June%2013%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20passed%20a%20series%20of%20orders%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20three-tier%20rural%20elections%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20it%20is%20surprised%20to%20note%20that%20even%20after%20the%20declaration%20of%20results%2C%20the%20state%20is%20not%20able%20to%20control%20the%20violence%20which%20has%20erupted%20in%20several%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20breach%20of%20peace%20lies%20with%20the%20state%20government.%20If%20the%20state%20government%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20safeguard%20its%20citizens%2C%20then%20it%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20matter%20to%20be%20taken%20note%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20also%20sought%20direction%20to%20the%20CBI%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20and%20conduct%20investigation%20into%20the%20violence%20and%20electoral%20malpractice%20and%20a%20forensic%20audit%20of%20the%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20polling%20booths%20and%20a%20forensic%20audit%20of%20the%20ballot%20papers%20by%20an%20independent%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20prayed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20be%20directed%20to%20forward%20a%20report%20to%20the%20central%20government%2