on't%20be%20easy%2C%20and%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20cakewalk%2C%20for%20the%20simple%20reason%20that%20there%20is%20a%20gulf%20between%20First%20Class%20cricket%20and%20Test%20cricket%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20the%20standards.%20But%20I%20think%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20will%20really%20do%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20JioCinema%20expert%20Abhinav%20Mukund%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CYashasvi%20is%20one%20of%20the%20more%20impressive%20young%20players%20coming%20out%20of%20this%20country%2C%20and%20I%20am%20excited%20to%20see%20how%20he%20goes%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20I%20feel%20he%20will%20respond%20well.%20Considering%20the%20conditions%20with%20the%20Dukes'%20ball%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20grass%2C%20I%20think%20Jaiswal%20will%20have%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20I%20think%20he%20has%20the%20technique%2C%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20mindset%20to%20play%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689165900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhe47ecko_yashasvi-jaiswal-twitter_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fit-wont-be-a-cakewalk-for-yashasvi-says-former-indian-cricketer-aakash-chopra-4200810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20is%20set%20to%20make%20his%20Test%20debut%20as%20an%20opener%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20today%20at%20Dominica%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fit-wont-be-a-cakewalk-for-yashasvi-says-former-indian-cricketer-aakash-chopra-4200810%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indi