0it%20has%20amassed%20nearly%206%2C000%20views%20on%20Twitter.%20Social%20media%20users%20dropped%20an%20array%20of%20reactions%20to%20the%20video.%20A%20user%20joked%2C%20%26quot%3BFree%20WWE%20inside%20train.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20make%20the%20mistake%20of%20calling%20Roshogulla%20rasgulla%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20fights%20allowed%2C%20the%20women%20in%20the%20society%20left%20so%20impatient%2C%20it's%20badly%20necessary%20where%20we%20find%20the%20patience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20user%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClinic%20%2B%20new%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fourth%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20incident%20of%20fighting%20inside%20local%20trains.%20Earlier%2C%20women%20were%20seen%20fighting%20inside%20the%20Mumbai%20local.%20In%20the%20clip%2C%20the%20women%20were%20seen%20engaging%20in%20a%20violent%20fight%20inside%20the%20ladies%20compartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689165720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fc7q5oofg_fight-inside-kolkata-local_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-women-passengers-slap-punch-and-pull-each-others-hair-inside-kolkata-local-4200958%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video%20shows%20women%20seen%20engaging%20in%20an%20ugly%20brawl%20inside%20the%20ladies%20compartment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-women-passengers-slap-punch-and-pull-each-others-hair-inside-kolkata-local-4200958%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-women-passengers-slap-punch-and-pull-each-others-hair-inside-kolkata-local-4200958%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-women-passengers-slap-punch-and-pull-each-others-hair-inside-kolkata-local-4200958%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20To%20Solve%20Delhi's%20Monsoon%20Mess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECome%20rain%20and%20our%20cities%20are%20reduced%20to%20flooded%20and%20damaged%20roads%2C%20overflowing%20drainage%2C%20and%20stinking%20garbage%20piles%20-%20a%20living%20hell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20problem%20seems%20to%20be%20poor%20planning%20and%20unbridled%20unauthorised%20constructions%2C%20which%20have%20ruined%20lakes%2C%20swamps%20and%20drainage%20systems%20in%20cities.%20Flooding%20can't%20be%20solved%20merely%20by%20desilting%20drains.%20Neither%20can%20it%20be%20resolved%20by%20the%20blame%20game%20between%20state%20governments%20and%20civic%20bodies%20after%20every%20deluge.%20The%20lack%20of%20coordination%20between%20government%20departments%20and%20municipal%20corporations%20is%20evident%20as%20the%20cleaning%2C%20desilting%20of%20drains%20and%20the%20maintenance%20of%20civic%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20different%20departments%20oversee%2C%20are%20often%20ill-managed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20citizens%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Chennai%2C%20along%20with%20those%20of%20newer%20metros%20like%20Bangalore%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20have%20been%20struggling%20with%20sewage-clogged%20roads%2C%20traffic%20nightmares%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20due%20to%20flooding%2C%20open%20manholes%2C%20and%20electrocution%20during%20monsoon.%20Cities%20in%20India%20are%20the%20propellers%20of%20economic%20growth%20and%20their%20contribution%20to%20GDP%20is%20around%2060%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20Iyer%2C%20Chief%20Policy%20and%20Insights%20officer%20at%20Janagraaha%2C%20based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20just%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%2C%20many%20of%20our%20urban%20systems%20often%20grapple%20with%20chronic%20capacity%20constraints%20and%20work%20on%20needs-basis%2C%20with%20SOPs%20and%20checks%2C%20in%20a%20responsive%20mode.%20Rains%20are%20annual%20but%20the%20patterns%20are%20changing%2C%20making%20wider%20war-room%20coordination%20between%20departments%2C%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20full%20planning%20reconsideration%2C%20imperative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rain%20lashed%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20causing%20floods%2C%20shutting%20down%20schools%20and%20disrupting%20normal%20life.%20A%20number%20of%20roads%20and%20underpasses%2C%20including%20the%20new%20Pragati%20Maidan%20tunnel%2C%20and%20Minto%20Bridge%2C%20were%20submerged%20in%20knee-deep%20water.%20The%20upscale%20parts%20of%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%2C%20the%20famous%20Khan%20market%2C%20and%20ministerial%20bungalows%20were%20in%20knee-deep%20water.%20Road%20cave-ins%20were%20democratically%20spread%20across%20the%20capital%2C%20not%20sparing%20VVIP%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlooding%20is%20a%20normal%2C%20recurring%20phenomenon%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20seem%20to%20be%20used%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20made%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20drainage%20system%20is%20not%20designed%20to%20tackle%20such%20high-intensity%20rainfall.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20why%20did%20he%20not%20realise%20it%20earlier%3F%20Is%20there%20no%20way%20to%20predict%20and%20prepare%20for%20such%20seasonal%20occurrences%3F%20Will%20a%20statement%20suffice%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20preparedness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20the%20government%20aspires%20to%20provide%20%3Cem%3Esmart%20cities%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20the%20capital%20of%20India%20is%20devoid%20of%20basic%20sanitation%2C%20hygiene%20and%20upkeep%20of%20public%20areas%20befitting%20its%20status%2C%20even%20during%20normal%2C%20predictable%20monsoon.%20We%20have%20been%20proudly%20hosting%20G20%20across%20cities%2C%20showcasing%20our%20'development'%20to%20the%20international%20delegates%2C%20but%20we%20are%20not%20prepared%20to%20preempt%20and%20mitigate%20the%20aftereffects%20of%20a%20predictable%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20embassies%20of%20over%20100%20countries%20see%20the%20sad%20state%20of%20affairs%20of%20our%20national%20capital%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20feeling%20embarrassed%2C%20the%20entire%20government%20machinery%20is%20busy%20passing%20the%20buck%20and%20shirking%20responsibility.%20%C2%A0As%20usual%2C%20citizens%20suffer%20and%20complain%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20their%20homes.%20A%20few%20weeks%20of%20discomfort.%20The%20monsoon%20will%20get%20over.%20And%20this%20too%20shall%20pass.%20Life%20moves%20on.%20One%20year%20of%20inaction%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20repeat%20of%20the%20entire%20episode%20next%20year.%20%3Cem%3EChalta%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20seems%20to%20reflect%20our%20%3Cem%3E'resilience'%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20isn't%20it%20the%20manifestation%20of%20our%20thick-skinned%20ignorance%20where%20mediocrity%20is%20the%20norm%20and%20accountability%20is%20absent%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20the%20solution%20elusive%3F%20Is%20the%20annual%20maintenance%20budget%20not%20allocated%20to%20the%20desilting%20and%20cleaning%20of%20drains%3F%20Is%20the%20design%20and%20size%20of%20drains%20outdated%20and%20incapable%20of%20taking%20the%20load%20of%20a%20growing%20population%3F%20Is%20the%20intent%20missing%3F%20Is%20political%20will%20subservient%20to%20the%20compulsions%20of%20the%20political%20economy%3F%20Why%20is%20it%20a%20norm%20to%20regularise%20unauthorized%20colonies%20constructed%20on%20encroached%20public%20drains%20to%20suit%20vote-bank%20politics%3F%20What%20could%20be%20the%20probable%20solutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20urgent%20relief%20in%20the%20immediate%20term%2C%20it%20is%20high%20time%20for%20preventive%20and%20systemic%20solutions.%20The%20stakes%20are%20high%20with%20Delhi%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20metropolis%20soon%3B%20it%20is%20also%20uniquely%20placed%2C%20having%20the%20strength%20of%20central%2C%20state%20and%20local%20bodies%2C%20and%20the%20best%20of%20technical%20knowledge%20and%20awareness.%20Climate%20change%20forces%20us%20to%20revisit%20planning%20and%20design%20considerations%2C%20not%20only%20of%20storm%20water%20drainage%20but%20also%20the%20city%20as%20a%20whole.%20The%20problem%20is%20regional%20but%20city%20authorities%20facing%20the%20risk%20of%20life%20and%20economy%20must%20be%20strengthened%20and%20empowered%20to%20operate%20fully%20towards%20the%20effects%20that%20are%20clearly%20located%20within%20their%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20adds%20Mr%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20widely%20acceptable%20solution%20is%20to%20modernize%2C%20redesign%20and%20reconstruct%20the%20drainage%20system%20and%20roads%20of%20Delhi.%20In%201976%2C%20IIT%20Delhi%20prepared%20the%20drainage%20master%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20still%20awaiting%20implementation%20despite%20the%20approval%20of%20several%20committees%20and%20governments%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%20This%20procrastination%20has%20impacted%20generations%20of%20Delhiites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20comes%20the%20solution%20that%20is%20known%20to%20all%20but%20conveniently%20ignored%20by%20the%20political%20class%20-%20the%20decongestion%20of%20Delhi.%20Hundreds%20of%20unauthorized%20colonies%2C%20constructed%20illegally%20by%20encroaching%20upon%20drains%2C%20lakes%20and%20government%20land%2C%20have%20choked%20the%20city's%20infrastructure.%20There%20is%20no%20outlet%20for%20rainwater%20to%20pass%20through%20drains%20due%20to%20massive%20concretisation.%20A%20humongous%20exercise%20of%20cleaning%20up%20these%20structures%20and%20rehabilitating%20occupants%20needs%20to%20be%20strategically%20done.%20If%20not%20planned%20and%20executed%20properly%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20nightmare%20for%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20country%20has%20seen%20expertise%20through%20the%20Public-Private-Partnership%20model%2C%20which%20is%20yielding%20results%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20sector.%20Construction%2C%20cleaning%2C%20desilting%2C%20repair%2C%20maintenance%20of%20the%20drainage%20system%20can%20be%20privatised%20by%20long-term%20contracts%20and%20supervised%20by%20government%20agencies.%20The%20inclusion%20of%20penalty%20clauses%20for%20inefficient%20service%20will%20ensure%20better%20maintenance%20than%20we%20see%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPWD%2C%20PWD%2C%20MCDs%2C%20NDMC%2C%20Delhi%20Metro%2C%20Delhi%20Cantonment%20Board%2C%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20and%20DDA%20are%20all%20strong%20government%20bodies%2C%20capable%20of%20being%20effective%20on%20their%20own%2C%20but%20by%20design%20lack%20the%20ability%20to%20collaborate%20and%20coordinate%20with%20each%20other%20to%20effectively%20deliver%20for%20public%20good.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhat%20Delhi%20needs%20is%20strong%20political%20will%2C%20joint%20coordination%20by%20government%20departments%2C%20planning%20and%20strong%20execution%20to%20overcome%20the%20recurrent%20pain%20inflicted%20on%20it%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689165600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhvfdtn1k_delhi-monsoon-ani-1200_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-to-solve-delhis-monsoon-mess-4200920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Come%20rain%20and%20our%20cities%20are%20reduced%20to%20flooded%20and%20damaged%20roads%2C%20overflowing%20drainage%2C%20and%20stinking%20garbage%20piles%20-%20a%20living%20hell.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-to-solve-delhis-monsoon-mess-4200920%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow