0men%20on%20alert%20with%20rifles%20pointed%20out%2C%20using%20binoculars%20to%20scan%20the%20surrounding%20area%20for%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20from%20both%20communities%20who%20man%20these%20bunkers%20call%20themselves%20village%20defence%20volunteers%20and%20claim%20their%20only%20motive%20is%20self-defence%2C%20police%20say%20many%20from%20both%20sides%20have%20died%20in%20the%20other's%20%26quot%3Bterritory%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20bunker%20is%20only%20for%20protection.%20Militants%20had%20fired%20again%2C%20so%20everyone%20in%20our%20village%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%20are%20worried%20about%20war.%20Hence%2C%20we%20built%20this%20bunker%20again%20to%20protect%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Arun%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20a%20village%20defence%20volunteer%20in%20Imphal%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoulian%2C%20a%20village%20defence%20volunteer%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20said%20the%20bunkers%20are%20needed%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20their%20villages.%20%26quot%3BActually%2C%20we%20are%20against%20dismantling%20of%20the%20bunkers.%20If%20all%20the%20bunkers%20are%20destroyed%2C%20how%20will%20we%20protect%20our%20villages%3F%20It%20won't%20be%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20our%20protection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20that%20schools%20from%20Classes%201%20to%208%20would%20reopen%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20had%20also%20said%20on%20July%203%20that%20bunkers%20built%20by%20both%20communities%20would%20be%20dismantled.%20While%20the%20authorities%20have%20acted%20on%20this%2C%20many%20of%20the%20bunkers%20that%20have%20been%20destroyed%20have%20simply%20been%20rebuilt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20border%20villages%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20locals%20led%20by%20women's%20groups%20are%20holding%20meetings%20to%20review%20their%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20holding%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20fallout%20of%20security%20forces%20dismantling%20our%20bunkers.%20Security%20personnel%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%2C%20dismantled%20all%20our%20bunkers%20and%20we%20allowed%20them%20to%20do%20it%20as%20we%20thought%20adequate%20security%20would%20be%20provided.%20But%2C%20other%20than%20posting%20eight%20Village%20Defence%20Force%20Personnel%2C%20the%20government%20has%20not%20given%20us%20enough%20security.%20We%20have%2C%20thus%2C%20reconstructed%20three%20bunkers%20for%20the%20village's%20defence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Damon%20Tombi%20Devi%2C%20president%20of%20one%20such%20group%20-%20the%20Moidangpok%20Apunba%20Meira%20Paibi%20Lup%20%C2%A0-%20in%20Imphal%20West.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hills%2C%20the%20tribal%20leadership%20has%20spoken%20out%20against%20operations%20to%20dismantle%20bunkers%20in%20villages.%20%26quot%3BOur%20villages%20have%20been%20attacked%20despite%20central%20security%20forces%20guarding%20their%20borders.%20If%20the%20bunkers%20are%20removed%2C%20our%20lives%20and%20villages%20will%20be%20under%20threat.%20We%20won't%20agree%20to%20the%20removal%20of%20bunkers%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20presence%20of%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20border%20villages%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ginza%20Vualzong%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20in%20Churachandpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20140%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20more%20than%203%2C000%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20began%20on%20May%203%20when%20a%20'Tribal%20Solidarity%20March'%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%20Over%2050%2C000%20people%20remain%20displaced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689165420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F8pg5am6_manipur-bunker-bunkers-650_625x300_12_July_23.j