0had%20been%20more%20time%2C%20a%20consensus%20could%20have%20been%20reached.%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%20our%20concerns%20were%20not%20taken%20seriously%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3EAFP%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20truly%20heartbroken%20that%20this%20council%20was%20unable%20to%20speak%20with%20a%20unanimous%20voice%20today%20in%20condemning%20what%20we%20all%20agree%20are%20deplorable%20acts%20of%20anti-Muslim%20hatred%20while%20also%20respecting%20freedom%20of%20expression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20U.N.%20in%20Geneva%2C%20Khalil%20Hasmi%2C%20accused%20the%20West%20of%20%E2%80%9Clip%20service%E2%80%9D%20to%20their%20commitment%20to%20prevent%20religious%20hatred.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThe%20opposition%20of%20a%20few%20in%20the%20room%20has%20emanated%20from%20their%20unwillingness%20to%20condemn%20the%20public%20desecration%20of%20the%20Holy%20Koran%20or%20any%20other%20religious%20book%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20lack%20political%2C%20legal%20and%20moral%20courage%20to%20condemn%20this%20act%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20minimum%20that%20the%20Council%20could%20have%20expected%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Hashmi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%94%B4BREAKING%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UN%3C%2Fa%3E%F0%9F%87%BA%F0%9F%87%B3%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20adopted%20draft%20resolution%20L.23%20(as%20orally%20revised)%20entitled%20%26quot%3BCountering%20religious%20hatred%20constituting%20incitement%20to%20discrimination%2C%20hostility%20or%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFull%20results%20of%20the%C2%A0vote%C2%A0at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%