in%20the%20past%20three%20days.%20The%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20issued%20warnings%20that%20more%20heavy%20downpour%20is%20expected%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Delhi%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241059%2Fpostmaster-women-himachal-pradesh-gramin-dak-sevak-letter-pension-delivery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%2C%20has%20seen%20incessant%20rains%20leading%20to%20landslides%20and%20flash%20floods%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20destruction.%20All%20major%20rivers%20including%20Beas%2C%20Ravi%2C%20Chenab%2C%20and%20Satluj%20are%20in%20spate%2C%20as%20vehicles%2C%20bridges%2C%20shops%2C%20and%20houses%20are%20being%20swept%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20tweet%20by%20DGP%20Satwant%20Atwal%2C%2030%20lives%20have%20been%20lost%20due%20to%20these%20rains%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20financial%20loss%20is%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIMD%20has%20issued%20a%20fresh%20red%20and%20orange%20alert%20in%20Himachal%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20red%20alert%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20Solan%2C%20Shimla%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20Kullu%2C%20Mandi%2C%20Kinnaur%2C%20and%20Lahaul%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours.%20An%20orange%20alert%20has%20been%20issued%20in%20Una%2C%20Hamirpur%2C%20Kangra%2C%20and%20Chamba.%20A%20flash%20flood%20warning%20has%20been%20issued%20for%20Mandi%2C%20Kinnaur%2C%20and%20Lahaul-Spiti%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20IMD%20Scientist%20Sandeep%20Kumar%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20on