0the%20trees%20and%20vegetation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trees%20grow%20throughout%20the%20building%2C%20creating%20transitional%20spaces%20between%20classroom%20clusters%2C%20courtyards%2C%20activity%20zones%2C%20walkways%2C%20and%20congregational%20areas%2C%20providing%20a%20green%20and%20refreshing%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20created%20various%20outdoor%20spaces%20for%20the%20students%20to%20learn%20in%20and%20from.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20have%20outdoor%20classrooms%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20observe%2C%20learn%20and%20interact%20with%20their%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20aims%20to%20bring%20the%20students%20close%20to%20nature.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-1-1688732411-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20outdoor%20classrooms%2C%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20channel%2C%20and%20a%20terrace%20that%20opens%20to%20tree%20tops.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Akanksha%20Gupta%3C%2F